b:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_18rem]","children":[["$","article",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"introduction","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-base leading-8 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200","children":"Formatting JSON looks cosmetic until you have to explain a broken payload to someone else. Readability is often the fastest route to understanding what actually went wrong."}]}],[["$","section","Readable structure reveals hidden mistakes",{"id":"readable-structure-reveals-hidden-mistakes","className":"interactive-panel rounded-[28px] p-6","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950 dark:text-slate-50","children":"Readable structure reveals hidden mistakes"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","p","Minified JSON hides relationships between keys, arrays, and nested objects. Once indentation is restored, missing values or misplaced brackets become much easier to spot.",{"children":"Minified JSON hides relationships between keys, arrays, and nested objects. Once indentation is restored, missing values or misplaced brackets become much easier to spot."}],["$","p","The improvement is not just visual comfort. It shortens the time between \"something is wrong\" and \"I know where to look next.\"",{"children":"The improvement is not just visual comfort. It shortens the time between \"something is wrong\" and \"I know where to look next.\""}]]}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300","children":[["$","li","Nesting becomes easier to scan",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","children":"Nesting becomes easier to scan"}],["$","li","Unexpected values stand out faster",{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3 dark:bg-slate-900","c